S.FORM: David Andersen nalecuhan i Melbourne, Victoria, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. David Andersen i 2002 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 2 ku uwac atu silsil 37, namapili' tu nu Atlanta Hawks putiput. 1 bulad 23 demiad, 1980 a mihca, David Andersen, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
